Mpaghara Nzukọ Nzukọ nke Nandigama bụ Mpaghara Ndepụta nke E debere na mpaghara NTR nke Andhra Pradesh nke na-ahọpụta ndị nnọchiteanya na Nzukọ Iwu nke Andhra Preadsh na India. Ọ bụ otu n'ime akụkụ asaa nke Vijayawada Lok Sabha.

Monditoka Jagan Mohana Rao bụ MLA nke ugbu a nke mpaghara ahụ, ebe ọ meriri ntuli aka 2019 Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly site na YSR Congress Party. As of 25 March 2019[update] na-erule ubochi iri abuo na ise na onwa Machị n'afo 2019[update], enwere ngụkọta nke ndị na-eme ntụli aka 195,011 na mpaghara ahụ. E guzobere mpaghara ahụ na afo 1955, dịka iwu Delimitation Orders (1955) si dị.
